Under staff but food is okay. Comfy environment for family gathering!
Spacious and food price is reasonable.

We came here with local friends, bought seafood first then took them here for cooking. Every dish was great with different Hong Kong cooking ways. The big calms steamed with garlic and green noodles was my favorite, and the mantis crayfish with deep fried minced garlic is also a traditional yummy dish. The lobster noodles was amazing good. And the dessert: black sesame film rolls, was very nice after a heavy meal. We had a great night here, and will come back again!

A new restaurant after renovation. Nice and comfy environment. Friendly staff and managers. Food is great. But of coz it is more expensive compared to the previous restaurant. The prices here are now similar to hoi teen.

reviews.text: Great place to shop for good quality seafood. Not the cheap kid thou

A small market with different kind of fresh seafoods, local catch or imported, which you can choose and bring it to restuarants opposite the street for cooking.  You can request for different styles of cooking.  If you are not familiar with the best way of cooking, I suggest you ask for professional help in the restaurants.
I had help with my friend's family ordering all the seafood that we got to hand pick, but everything was delicious. It was an amazing experience to have with friends and family. Thank you!
Seafood market and seafood restaurants
Great place for seafood!

reviews.text: 食物不錯但價格算高，不推薦。
三聖村街市海鮮市場，四處酒家林立，大多以海鮮為主打。是屯門區出名的海鮮食肆地。
龍蛇混雜，不宜久留。
海鮮合理價連代煮每人约400元今次三人购了海蝦 靑班 算子
今天，天氣好好是星期六， 比想像中人很少 ， 覺得冷清清 ，不過很舒服 ，食嘢方便一般啦 ，價錢都唔平 ， 海鮮種類市區都會有這些貨品 ，如果在市區都可以食到 ，沒有什麼特別

reviews.text: 不錯，服務好格調好價錢跟大牌檔差不多的酒樓。(三聖海鮮以大牌檔為主的)
打開茶壺蓋要先有人沖水 冇嘢我話佢呀打開茶壺蓋呀照先有人沖水呀點呀點呀
晚飯空調不足，要自備風扇潑涼，價格中上，可自攜海鮮到來加工。
飲茶,環境好,特色點心好味道。有泊車位,當然,因為佢就係三聖商場上面, 下有二層都係車位。再遠少少都有其他可泊車地點。
早茶出品不錯、服務尚可、地方寛敞
